timeline.description:
Procurement:
- Collection Center: CC-SF-101

Processing:
- Cleaning: Manual dry cleaning
- Drying: Sun-dried at 25°C for 72 hours (Final Moisture: 8.5%)
- Grinding: Coarse

Quality & Safety:
- Inspection: Good color, strong aroma, consistent texture.

Storage & Dispatch:
- Stored for 14 days in Cool, dry, dark warehouse
